default DECC provides sustainability requirements for biomass including GHG requirements and in addition there are specific sustainability requirements being im
defaultplemented under the RHI. An online tool - the UK 
defaultBiomass &amp; Biogas Carbon Calculator
default is provided by OFGEM to enable generators and others to 
defaultassess the emissions associated with biomass electricity and heat generation. The tool takes into account the emissions across the bio-energy lifecycle from cultivation of biomass to processing and transport. The calculator should be 
defaultreviewed on a regular 
defaultbasis to ensure the process takes into account the most up-to-date information available on the bio-energy lifecycle.
